1. What is Betalingsservice?
:SKRSLUT.
:SWISS8.
.br
Betalingsservice is a payment service which enables the customer to pay
bills in DKK to creditors registered in the system. Once the customer has
given a BS mandate to his or her creditor, the creditor is authorised
to collect payments from from the customer's account.
.br
Betalingsservice is a system designed for recurring payments, but the
creditor may also execute one-off payments and pay e.g. excess amounts
paid on account into the customer's account.
.sp 5mm
.kp off
.kp on
:SWISS10.
:FED.
2. Definitions
.sp 3mm
:SWISS8.
:FED.
2.1 Refusal
:SKRSLUT.
.br
:SWISS8.
If payment is refused, the system will not execute the payment
transaction. The customer may refuse a future payment in accordance
with the provisions set out in clause 8.1.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
:FED.
2.2 Banking day
:SKRSLUT.
.br
:SWISS8.
Banking days are all days except Saturdays, Sundays, Danish public
holidays, the Friday after Ascension Day, 5 June, 24 December and 31
December.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
:FED.
2.3 Betalingsservice mandate (BS mandate)
:SKRSLUT.
.br
A BS mandate is an agreement between the customer and a creditor
authorising the creditor to collect payments from the customer using
Betalingsservice. The customer may give a BS mandate directly to the
creditor or through &BANKNAVN. acting on behalf of the creditor.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
:FED.
2.4 Payment date
:SKRSLUT.
.br
The payment date is the day on which the amount is debited to the
customer's account. Payments are executed on banking days only.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
:FED.
2.5 Betalingsservice prenotification
:SKRSLUT.
.br
The Betalingsservice prenotification lists the following month's
Betalingsservice payments from the customer's account. The customer
will receive his or her prenotification electronically or by ordinary
mail just before the change of month.
.sp 3mm
.kp off
.kp on
:FED.
2.6 Electronic payment information
:SKRSLUT.
.br
The customer may choose to receive electronic payment information in
his or her online banking system or electronic mailbox.
